}

query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Vendor
  ดึงข้อมูลผู้ขายรายการเดียวตาม ID

  Retrieves a single vendor/supplier record by its unique identifier.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Vendor ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.vendor:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "code": "VND-2024-0001",
      "name": "Siam Fresh Co., Ltd.",
      "description": "Fresh produce and food ingredients supplier",
      "note": "Preferred fresh produce supplier",
      "business_type": {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4e",
        "name": "Food Supplier"
      },
      "tax_profile_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4f",
      "tax_profile_name": "VAT 7%",
      "tax_rate": 7,
      "is_active": true,
      "info": [],
      "vendor_address": [
        {
          "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c50",
          "address_type": "mailing_address",
          "address_line1": "88/12 Mu 4, Phahonyothin Road",
          "city": "Pathum Thani",
          "postal_code": "12120",
          "country": "Thailand"
        }
      ],
      "vendor_contact": [
        {
          "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c51",
          "name": "Wannapa Srisuwan",
          "email": "wannapa.s@siamfresh.co.th",
          "phone": "0812345678",
          "is_primary": true
        }
      ],
      "audit": {
        "created": {
          "at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
          "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
          "name": "John Doe"
        },
        "updated": {
          "at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
          "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567891",
          "name": "Jane Smith"
        }
      }
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.vendor:view` permission |
  | 404 | Vendor not found |
}

